 <title>Customizing the Universal Gateway</title>

 <para>The gateway includes a complete, stable application programming
 interface, designed to allow you to customize the gateway as required.
 Customization of the gateway may be necessary if you need to perform complex
 server interactions or intensive data transformations, and stock handlers,
 filters and expressions provided by the gateway are too basic to meet the
 task.</para>
 
